{"tid":60231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美啲人點解仲會除夕倒數","createTime":"2016-12-30T09:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T17:40:04.000Z","uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0fe396ff013115c52975e9e3af01f7f32c5bd37","tid":60231,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"依加歐美受恐襲機會咁高，isis成日搞事，前排德國聖誕市集先有恐襲<br />\n恐怖組織一定會睇中人群聚集嘅地方同日子，報復打擊恐怖主義國家<br />\n即使國家安全保安工作做得好，仍然有受襲風險，但啲人仍出去倒數，例如美國時代廣場每年都有百萬人慶祝，佢地真係唔驚？<br />\n取消除夕倒數又話向惡勢力退縮，但人命尤關，點解仲要舉行倒數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人意見，歡迎各位討論，抒發見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb08cfdff303a27fb6e9e7882c3773be35dad37","tid":60231,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bd752987eb2fb9438b64b9540cb89d6efbc775","tid":60231,"uid":69057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"呢世都有恐怖分子呢世都唔倒數？"},{"pid":"16bfe29ec53871b45ac2fce75710180c5a18fc2c","tid":60231,"uid":35133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"恐怖份子都去左倒數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bd771f210fadb2e93caad0d266def44ebc6689","tid":60231,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"恐怖份子就係想你驚"},{"pid":"abe8adb286dc4327ce978775d72dbfd1a8ef87b0","tid":60231,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"是福不是禍，是禍躲不過。<br />\n恐怖份子要做嘢，任何時候都得，唔使擇日。"},{"pid":"a39cae7abb8112f8d279833fec7296201f4e35b2","tid":60231,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢世都有恐怖分子呢世都唔倒數？</blockquote><br />\n<br /